AffinityLive,is,an,online,project,management,and,client,relationship,management,platform,AffinityLive,can,be,used,to,manage,sales,track,projects,and,keep,track,of,client,relationships,The,AffinityLive,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,AffinityLive,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,company,information,creating,and,managing,customer,data,and,tracking,and,managing,issues